# Official MIMIC-CXR-JPG layout (PhysioNet partial download):
#   datasets/mimic/p{subject_id}/s{study_id}/*.jpg
#   datasets/mimic/p{subject_id}/s{study_id}.txt   (radiology report)
#
# Abdominal CT demo (source=mimic, for endocrinology / gastroenterology):
#   datasets/mimic/endocrine_ct_001/s001/imaging.nii.gz
#   Fetch: python scripts/fetch_demo_datasets.py --mimic-ct
#
# Example CXR:
#   datasets/mimic/p10000980/s54577367/*.jpg
#
# Scanned as source=mimic_cxr, collection=MIMIC-CXR-JPG (not CT).
# Rebuild manifest: python scripts/build_mimic_cxr_manifest.py
